metadata.name: Musketon & Dirty Belgium: WEB32, Creative Intervention NFT airdrop 1
metadata.description:
Artists: Musketon & Dirty Belgium  
Supported by: Thomas De Ben  
Title: WEB32, Creative Intervention NFT airdrop 1  
File type: JPEG image  
Colour space: RGB  
Dimensions: 2160px x 1800px

About: 

This artwork is a digitalised live mural made during the first edition of the WEB32 convention the 9th of June 2022. Each visitor received a digitalised NFT edition of the artwork as a memento collectible and delivered on a physical pre-generated NFT wallet by Thomas De Ben (Never Forget Tomorrow).

More info:  
www.neverforgettomorrow.be
